        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "fix(web): polish browse listing pages",
        "body": "## Summary\n\nThis PR updates the browse/listing experience across Home, Skills, Plugins, and Publishers. It replaces the old sidebar-heavy browse UI with shared top controls, standardizes mobile search reveal/close behavior, tightens list/grid layouts, and adds topic/category handling that behaves better across narrow viewports.\n\n## What changed\n\n| Area | Updates |\n| --- | --- |\n| Shared browse controls | Added reusable tabs, sort select, category select, search trigger/panel/input, topic chips, and view toggle primitives. Removed the old BrowseSidebar component. |\n| Search behavior | Home, Skills, and Plugins use the same revealable search pattern. Publishers keeps the desktop search reveal while omitting search on mobile. The X closes and clears consistently where the revealable search is available. |\n| Mobile/narrow layout | Category controls flex to available width, search sits to the right, topics are hidden on narrow screens, category columns are hidden where they cost too much space, and list rows truncate instead of clipping. |\n| Topics | Skills and Plugins list rows now show topic chips on roomy viewports, limited to two. Topic chip styling is quieter and less distracting. |\n| Skeletons | Home listing loading now uses the same list skeleton as Skills/Plugins, keeping the first loading state closer to the final list layout. |\n| Skills | Top browse tabs now separate All, Top, Most starred, and Featured; secondary sort stays available on wider layouts. List/grid cards share the updated metadata hierarchy. |\n| Plugins | Adds the All/Official/Updated tab model, list/grid polish, official badge handling, topic limit, and infinite load-more behavior. |\n| Publishers | Adds shared browse controls, list/grid polish, the Officials tab, search debounce/submit parity, and official publisher pagination support. Mobile tabs use content-aware sizing, and directory rows reduce to avatar, name, handle, and right-aligned installs. |\n| Supporting utilities | Adds small text truncation and media-query helpers used by browse rows/cards. Updates public publisher item types so publisher cards can render richer published-item previews. |\n| Cleanup | Removes unused browse/sidebar exports and trims stale helpers/tests around the old listing UI. |\n\n\n## Visual QA\n\nCaptured from a real local ClawHub instance at `http://127.0.0.1:11170` against the public Convex read backend. Full gallery: [cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now](https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/).\n\n| Coverage | Count |\n| --- | ---: |\n| Screens | 4: Home, Skills, Plugins, Publishers |\n| Themes | 2: dark and light |\n| Closed-search states | 56 screenshots |\n| Desktop search-open states | 16 screenshots |\n| Total embedded screenshots | 72 screenshots |\n\n<details open>\n<summary>Home listing · dark</summary>\n\nClosed search states:\n\n| 1920 list | 1920 grid | 1440 list | 1440 grid | Tablet list | Tablet grid | Mobile list |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1920.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1920.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark list Desktop 1920 closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-grid-1920.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-grid-1920.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark grid Desktop 1920 closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1440.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1440.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark list Desktop 1440 closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-grid-1440.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-grid-1440.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark grid Desktop 1440 closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-tablet.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-tablet.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark list Tablet closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-grid-tablet.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-grid-tablet.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark grid Tablet closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-mobile.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-mobile.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark list Mobile closed\" /></a> |\n\nDesktop-only search-open states:\n\n| 1920 search open | 1440 search open |\n|---|---|\n| <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1920-search-open.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1920-search-open.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark list Desktop 1920 search-open\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1440-search-open.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/dark/home-list-1440-search-open.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing dark list Desktop 1440 search-open\" /></a> |\n\n</details>\n\n<details open>\n<summary>Home listing · light</summary>\n\nClosed search states:\n\n| 1920 list | 1920 grid | 1440 list | 1440 grid | Tablet list | Tablet grid | Mobile list |\n|---|---|---|---|---|---|---|\n| <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/light/home-list-1920.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/light/home-list-1920.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing light list Desktop 1920 closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/light/home-grid-1920.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/light/home-grid-1920.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing light grid Desktop 1920 closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/light/home-list-1440.png\"><img src=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/light/home-list-1440.png\" width=\"190\" alt=\"Home listing light list Desktop 1440 closed\" /></a> | <a href=\"https://cozy-bodhi-5kcw.here.now/light/home-grid-1440.png\"><img